item.title: Professional Experience

item.description: During Covid-19 pandemics I had to compile my work as a Computer Scientist. To share it with other people around the world in projects that I am (or might be) involved. I hope that my readers here, are also creating amazing software! Special Motivation I have built this website to learn Hugo (a very very nice static website creator coded using “Go”). This site is published at gihub.io, a free place to host web content like this!
